# Phase 5 Implementation Summary

## Database Optimization (SQL Indexes)

To ensure the system remains performant as the dataset grows, run the following SQL commands to create the necessary indexes. These indexes target the most common query paths identified in Phase 5 (Search, Audit Logs, and Dashboards).

```sql
-- Indexes for AuditLog table
CREATE INDEX idx_audit_logs_timestamp ON audit_logs(timestamp);
CREATE INDEX idx_audit_logs_user_id ON audit_logs(user_id);
CREATE INDEX idx_audit_logs_entity_type ON audit_logs(entity_type);

-- Indexes for Event table (for Search and Filtering)
CREATE INDEX idx_events_status ON events(status);
CREATE INDEX idx_events_created_at ON events(created_at);
CREATE INDEX idx_events_created_by ON events(created_by);
-- Trigram indexes might be better for LIKE searches in PostgreSQL, 
-- but for standard SQLite/SQL, these cover the basics.
```

## N+1 Query Elimination
Every dashboard and list view has been refactored to use `joinedload()`. This ensures that related data (like User or Approvals) is fetched in a single efficient query instead of one query per row.

Example from [faculty.py](file:///d:/EDUCATION/Work/SDLC%20Project/Event%20Planner%20and%20Approval%20System%20-%20Phase%205/app/blueprints/faculty.py):
```python
query = Event.query.options(joinedload(Event.creator)).filter_by(status=EventStatus.Pending_Faculty)
```

## Search & Pagination Integration
A new utility [app/utils/search.py](file:///d:/EDUCATION/Work/SDLC%20Project/Event%20Planner%20and%20Approval%20System%20-%20Phase%205/app/utils/search.py) provides [apply_search_and_pagination](file:///d:/EDUCATION/Work/SDLC%20Project/Event%20Planner%20and%20Approval%20System%20-%20Phase%205/app/utils/search.py#4-45). This has been integrated into:
- Student Dashboard
- Faculty Dashboard
- Dept Head Dashboard
- Admin Users View
- Admin Audit Logs View

## Currency Formatting
All monetary values now use the Indian Rupee symbol (**₹**). 
- A custom Jinja2 filter `| format_inr` has been registered in [app/__init__.py](file:///d:/EDUCATION/Work/SDLC%20Project/Event%20Planner%20and%20Approval%20System%20-%20Phase%205/app/__init__.py).
- Form labels in [app/forms/event_form.py](file:///d:/EDUCATION/Work/SDLC%20Project/Event%20Planner%20and%20Approval%20System%20-%20Phase%205/app/forms/event_form.py) have been updated.
- All templates use the filter for consistent rendering (e.g., `{{ event.budget | format_inr }}`).

## Audit Logging
The [AuditLog](file:///d:/EDUCATION/Work/SDLC%20Project/Event%20Planner%20and%20Approval%20System%20-%20Phase%205/app/models/audit.py#15-32) system captures every significant action:
- **LOGIN / LOGOUT / REGISTER**
- **EVENT CREATE / EDIT**
- **APPROVAL / REJECTION / CHANGES REQUESTED**

Logs are viewable by Admins at `/admin/audit-logs`.
